01:05:18.901 --> 01:05:21.148
Podignite me.

01:05:27.726 --> 01:05:29.426
Dobro.

01:05:30.469 --> 01:05:32.469
Miranda.

01:05:39.824 --> 01:05:41.824
Gore, gore.

